{"tid":747911,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實不能用理據駁斥人，只能話對方係五毛呀自乾五呀跟住屌人老母呢種習慣應該要戒了","createTime":"2018-07-18T18:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T11:00:50.000Z","uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31d2cddf3f71a6b847a4f3cc290e3fc31b2376de","tid":747911,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"幻想呢度係城市論壇（其實連登人流同記者數量分分鐘仲多），你一開口就「你隻死五毛/死自乾五，我屌你老母呀」跟住完全提供唔到理據，咁嘅水平作為嗰啲好憎中共但又因心急儲錢變性於是做ACO賺錢嘅人放工上時事台發洩就無問題，但如果要幹一番偉業的話，唔係歧視講粗口，起碼你講嘢都要先有point"},{"pid":"c278481155bd871861b8368c03d4db79ec3bf637","tid":747911,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"好似啤梨同亨利咁<br />\n我聽啤梨講十分鐘<br />\n咁啱佢閙緊黃碧雲<br />\n但點解要屌，佢又講唔出<br />\n我聽你講六個字粗口就會high咩？<br />\n於是我以後都唔會聽<br />\n而亨利雖然一樣有粗口<br />\n但人哋有point有cap圖有證據<br />\n你要幹一番大事<br />\n招人同籌款都係靠自己把口<br />\n可能圈內人會好buy啤梨<br />\n但要圈外人出錢出力<br />\n就要學下亨利了"},{"pid":"c807561aae54992589d22757fe1732d3da463286","tid":747911,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eb3c9bf1f5db757151018d58ed371ebc2a8848","tid":747911,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20406697a3c2302e5837b94796394318536382ce","tid":747911,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/190046_53c29d20b239d82efcf06453428b082c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F190046_53c29d20b239d82efcf06453428b082c.png&h=30372028&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/190047_cbec89629c2e6c611e891cf405011b8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F190047_cbec89629c2e6c611e891cf405011b8a.png&h=1a144e55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/190047_26cfefd34788b1920535d437882189e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F190047_26cfefd34788b1920535d437882189e6.png&h=7eddd307&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}